{"tid":809090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國駐港領事：陳浩天言論不影響美國對香港的政策","createTime":"2018-09-07T01:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T05:36:02.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f0cde0b6a526fc0af15839b88973e303f2e9614b","tid":809090,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1028512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1028512&d=9b3%2B2YHVjZQkmEDiOr2KCy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7974d1f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1028512</a><br />\n<br />\n美國駐港領事：陳浩天言論不影響美方對港政策<br />\n05.09.2018 12:26<br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天再次去信美國華府，呼籲美國國務院取消《香港政策法》，指政策法在制訂時，假設了香港政制將在回歸後步向民主，但目前香港政制日漸背離民主，故香港早已喪失《政策法》下給予特殊待遇的基礎。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐港總領事唐偉康指，香港現時所享的自主，仍然高於政策法的要求，事件不會影響美國對中國和香港的態度，又指今年是美國駐港總領事館在本港成立的175周年，美國和香港一直在貿易和其他議題上，保持密切和良好的關係。"},{"pid":"a38c9d237fdf475463edd503a1e16dfa93100a6d","tid":809090,"uid":139700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"失望，明明充公共狗美資會多過n倍伊朗啲錢"},{"pid":"b5c09098e73d1033d003fb9fbac95e36ea7beed7","tid":809090,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:39:38.000Z","msg":"cable有片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=wnIXa9OlVQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D3%26v%3DwnIXa9OlVQA&d=9b3%2B2YHVjZQkmEDiOr2KCy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=31cfc6f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=wnIXa9OlVQA</a>"},{"pid":"062dda5d1bc99589a5735c7e7405a6a73d81c704","tid":809090,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:39:42.000Z","msg":"真可笑 以為自己是誰"},{"pid":"f094f376e3ad1cff